comment_data.body:
It is as if when Android Studio installed on your machine it didn't include all of the required debugger class files.  I assume it happens every time you try to debug, and it is not a sporadic issue?  Have you had success debugging with other IJ/ AS versions on this machine?

@stevemessick who has been working on the Flutter Plugin AS support.
Try uninstalling and reinstalling. I cannot reproduce it
Closing issue, reinstalling should fix the issue.
